g\u2011distance flights, and that the only serious red flags for Candidate\u202fC are communication\u2011related rather than outright hostility, Candidate\u202fC still offers the best overall balance of the required criteria.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
